headline: Trane Technologies plc (TT) is Benefitting From Several Long-Term Secular Trends
summary: Parnassus Investments, an investment management company, released the “Parnassus Mid Cap Fund” third quarter 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In the third quarter, the Fund (Investor Shares) returned 8.55% (net of fees) outperforming the Russell Midcap Index’s 6.54% return. Stock selection in Health Care sector drove the outperformance […]

headline: Trane, Northern Illinois University partner for energy infrastructure improvements
summary: The upgrades, which include LED lighting, EV charging stations and solar photovoltaic installations, can cut greenhouse gas emissions and energy consumption by 11% and over 26%, respectively, Trane Technologies says.
